                     <interp inst="t18170917-96-person659" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prisoner's brother; he bought me a jacket and a waistcoat at Lyons's shop - I paid for them; as we were going home, he shewed me the breeches, and said he took them from the shop.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I bought them of a Jew.</p>
